the program reinstated its previous nfl today title on september 21 , 1975 , with former wbbm - tv and knxt sportscaster/anchorman brent musburger ( previously a play - by-play announcer for cbs ) serving as host , former nfl player irv cross as an analyst , and former miss america phyllis george as one of the reporters .

there she is , miss america : this 1971 winner co - hosted " the nfl today " for cbs from 1975 to 1984

